    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i dont really have time for the doctor right now lol. it doesnt look like it's broken or anything, just really puffy. if i just keep it iced and wrapped up for like 48 hours, do you think that'll be enough to fix it? i really just want to avoid a clinic visit if i can.",
