      "content": "okay but if I keep it elevated and keep the compression wrap tight like you said, isn't that basically the same thing as getting it checked? i feel like if it was actually broken i would have heard a snap or something. i'd rather just take some ibuprofen and power through it for a couple days than waste money on an x-ray if it's just a bad sprain. you think that's a safe bet for now?",
